videos.description: Matthew Moyer gets the offensive rebound and finds Tyus Battle who knocks in a 3-pointer in the first half against Buffalo.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Moyer keeps it alive for a nice triple

videos.description: Wes Clark dribbles past defenders and hits an easy field goal to put the Bulls ahead of Syracuse 53-52 in the second half.
videos.headline: Clark knocks in jumper to put Buffalo ahead

videos.description: Oshae Brissett cuts through Buffalo defenders and draws contact but finishes the layup in the second half.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Brisset shows off with Eurostep and -1
